{"tid":2512619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玻璃樽版可口可樂原來已經停咗產","createTime":"2021-05-02T01:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T02:20:18.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"624dfe8d155af8931b6ee75c6f62f75d463c9269","tid":2512619,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPhB7DR5HdEAztch4cwt8mVmYoJqkdgQSURLKkxTdgdD9?filename=6Ysh26D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Ysh26D.gif&h=c45e0438&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7448a212c18a247df586c24dca597fa65ba32b4c","tid":2512619,"uid":237222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:14:44.000Z","msg":"轉物料再出嘛 唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bd045327b609d1a7e13bd9e6e7384bc2a39a5a","tid":2512619,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:16:43.000Z","msg":"玻璃樽可口可樂將停產　新設計更環保　可樂迷：或出超薄玻璃樽<br />\n<br />\n「可口可樂」推出樽裝汽水多年，生產商香港太古可口可樂宣布將於今年第二季起暫別玻璃樽包裝，改良後設計將加入環保元素，並於2022年重新登場。<br />\n<br />\n香港太古可口可樂表示，「可口可樂」及其他系列汽水，玻璃樽裝將於今年第二季起停產，新設計將引入更多環保元素，可回收重用之餘，亦將包含再生玻璃物料，樽身將更輕量。新設計將於2022年重新登場。期間會繼續推出罐裝及膠樽裝汽水。<br />\n<br />\n香港可口可樂收藏俱樂部方會長（Wago）向《香港01》表示，自上月起與其他可樂迷到士多買可樂，已得悉供應商將不會再補貨，而現售的玻璃樽裝可樂將於５月停售。據了解，可口可樂今年第二季有新的生產線，生產新的樽裝可口可樂。<br />\n<br />\n方會長表示，得悉在泰國生產的樽裝可口可樂已變成「超薄玻璃樽裝」，泰國的新玻璃樽裝可樂「容量約250毫升，玻璃樽變得好薄」，設計會引入更多環保元素，可回收重用。<br />\n<br />\n「現時的玻璃樽裝可口可樂是最經典的，用玻璃樽裝充氣量亦更好，令汽水更好飲。」他又擔心，香港一旦通關會引來不少收藏家及炒家到港掃貨，現在他與其他可樂迷都已開始外出尋找一些回收痕跡輕微的玻璃樽裝汽水作收藏，以「原水原蓋」方式保留，因為已是買少見少。<br />\n<br />\nLuke又以香港為例，現時轉手價值最高的是開廠時首批生產玻璃樽，「（一個）至少過二萬，有人放出嚟都好快被人買晒。」據他所說，開廠樽指的是1991年落成沙田可樂廠首批可樂樽，限量100個，當時出席的嘉賓可獲一支。"},{"pid":"5015b17698b81017e92cff3cf8f28b64f882e3c1","tid":2512619,"uid":266519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔係化，去舊士多一定對番支～"},{"pid":"1a6f896e1c63cacf0f2590462836a5c4c62becaa","tid":2512619,"uid":35507,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"玻璃樽版最好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc128bcef13e1199333ecb64fde9c82d7ab55010","tid":2512619,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:24:39.000Z","msg":"早期既先有得炒"},{"pid":"a251af74e6920325a6acf94d38150128177e9ced","tid":2512619,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc128bcef13e1199333ecb64fde9c82d7ab55010","tid":2512619,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:24:39.000Z","msg":"早期既先有得炒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:27:19.000Z","msg":"咁可樂個玻璃樽真係幾好睇既"},{"pid":"9480ae3121a89d581738b319d6c6adbc4d53ac23","tid":2512619,"uid":73310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a6f896e1c63cacf0f2590462836a5c4c62becaa","tid":2512619,"uid":35507,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"玻璃樽版最好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:29:38.000Z","msg":"買打食玻璃大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34e5f956daa305eaef4387e33f10c8f36f3d571","tid":2512619,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5015b17698b81017e92cff3cf8f28b64f882e3c1","tid":2512619,"uid":266519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep